data.description: Are you looking for a completely remodeled, 3 bedroom, 2 bath home in Iowa sitting on half an acre and UNDER 200k?? Look no further! Located in a quiet subdivision, this beautifully updated home was redone from the studs after the hurricane. With a split open floor plan, new roof, new sheetrock, fresh paint, new privacy fence, new butcher block island, new laminate flooring throughout, updated fixtures, & updated bathrooms. The master suite comes equipped with bay windows, tray ceiling, & his/her sinks! With a spacious fence in back yard, back deck perfect for entertaining and those afternoon BBQs!  This home qualifies for Rural Development, which means 100% financing! Located in flood zone X so flood insurance typically not required. Don't miss out, schedule your showing today!
